org.gvsig.gpe.kml.parser.v21.features
Class FolderBinding

java.lang.Object
  org.gvsig.gpe.kml.parser.v21.features.FolderBinding

public class FolderBinding
extends java.lang.Object

This class parses a Folder tag. Example: 

 
 <Folder>
 <Placemark>
 <name>CDATA example</name>
 <description>Description example</description>
 <Point>
 <oordinates>102.595626,14.996729</coordinates>
 </Point>
 </Placemark>
 </Folder>

Author:
Jorge Piera LLodrá (jorge.piera@iver.es)
See Also:
http://code.google.com/apis/kml/documentation/kml_tags_21.html#folder
